import React from 'react';
import {
  ArtickesLikeImg, ArticlesDate, ArticlesDescription,
  ArticlesHeader,
  ArticlesInfo, ArticlesItem, ArticlesLikesCount,
  ArticlesStats, ArticlesTag, ArticlesTagsWrap,
  articlesTitle, ArticlesUserImage, ArticlesUserInfo, ArticlesUserInfoGroup, ArticlesUsername,
} from '../../styled-components';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import { articleUrl } from '../../routes';
import disabledLikeSrc from '../../images/like-disabled.svg';
import userDefaultImgSrc from '../../images/user-default-img.svg';


const Article = () => {

  return (
    <ArticlesItem>
      <ArticlesInfo>
        <ArticlesHeader>
          <Link style={articlesTitle} to={articleUrl}>
            Some article title
          </Link>
          <ArticlesStats>
            <ArtickesLikeImg src={disabledLikeSrc} />
            <ArticlesLikesCount>10</ArticlesLikesCount>
          </ArticlesStats>
        </ArticlesHeader>
        <ArticlesTagsWrap>
          <ArticlesTag>tag</ArticlesTag>
          <ArticlesTag>someTag</ArticlesTag>
        </ArticlesTagsWrap>

        <ArticlesDescription>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit,
          sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
          Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco
          laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat
        </ArticlesDescription>
      </ArticlesInfo>

      <ArticlesUserInfo>
        <ArticlesUserInfoGroup>
          <ArticlesUsername>John Doe</ArticlesUsername>
          <ArticlesDate>March 5, 2020</ArticlesDate>
        </ArticlesUserInfoGroup>
        <ArticlesUserImage src={userDefaultImgSrc} />
      </ArticlesUserInfo>
    </ArticlesItem>
  )
}

export default Article;
